content.title: Welcome To JP's Ark!
content.text:
JP's Ark is a cluster, self hosted in the UK. 

All the hardware is owned and this ensures the longevity of the servers.

Maps in the cluster:

The Island
Scorched Earth
Aberration
Extinction
The Center
Ragnarok
Club Ark

Mods:

Automated Ark
Utilities Plus
Arkitect Structures Remastered
Death Recovery Item Tool
ArkNav
JP's Baby Manager
Solo Farm
Custom Dino Levels
